review.reviewBody:
The first time I made exactly as recipe and it was good.  Tonight I made this with a few additions  and it was excellent.  Added:
Used dry onion soup mix (instead of onion)
1/4 - 1/2 c dry red wine;
1 tsp. thyme;
sliced fresh mushrooms;
1 tsp better than bullion beef base in 1 c boiling water;
1 tbs Worcestershire sauce;
thickened with some of the sauce and corn starch
*used cream of mushroom soup with garlic;
Served over mashed potatoes
